            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"travel-time-distribution\">Travel time distribution</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">For a constant velocity model and a single source, travel times\nshould be proportional to source\u2013receiver distance.</span></span>"
