            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"summary\">Summary</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The complete file-free workflow in four lines:</span>\n<div class=\"language-python codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">model</span>   <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">pyswmp</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">create_constant_velocity_model</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">...</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">opts</span>    <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">pyswmp</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">TrackerOptions</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">coordinate_system</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">extract_raypaths</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">tracker</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">pyswmp</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">WaveFrontTracker</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">model</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">opts</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">result</span>  <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">tracker</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">forward</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">sources</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">receivers</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Next notebooks cover:</span>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>02</strong> \u2014 Validating accuracy against the analytical great circle solution</li>\n<li><strong>03</strong> \u2014 Real-world multipathing with the Australian velocity model</li>\n<li><strong>04</strong> \u2014 Frechet sensitivity kernels and the Jacobian matrix</li>\n<li><strong>05</strong> \u2014 Parallel execution for multi-source problems</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
